snippet.title: Court of Darkness Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming soon to iOS & Android!

It all begins with a kiss.

Step into a world of magical romance and dark fantasy, where power you never knew you possessed waits to be released. 
Now, princes from another realm will do anything to claim it for themselves. 

However, they don't realize how much more to you there is... and by the time they do, their hearts will be irrevocably yours.
